nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 157 is the 135th issue of Star Wars Insider magazine and the sixty-fifth published by Titan Magazines. It was released on April 21, 2015.

Darth Vader and the Emperor feature in an all-new tale exclusive to this issue. We celebrate the 10th anniversary of Revenge of the Sith with exclusive interviews with the cast and crew! Plus: We profile Han Solo's journey from rogue to rebel and share the experiences of the Star Wars prequel generation!
